Retrieve all Todos for a user	GET		/users/{username}/todos
Delete a Todo of a User			DELETE  /users/{username}/todos/{id}
Edit a Todo						PUT 	/users/{username}/todos/{id}
Create a new Todo				POST	/users/{username}/todos

GET all todos
http://localhost:8080/users/{username}/todos
http://localhost:8080/users/in28minutes/todos

GET one todo
http://localhost:8080/users/in28minutes/todos/1

DELETE
http://localhost:8080/users/in28minutes/todos/1

